Subject: [PATCH 4.19 082/219] Bluetooth: Workaround directed advertising bug in Broadcom controllers
Date:   Sun, 29 Dec 2019 18:18:04 +0100
Message-Id: <20191229162517.979966167@linuxfoundation.org>
